videos.description: Villanova's Eric Paschall explodes past the defender and throws down the huge jam.
videos.headline: Paschall throws down the big-time dunk

videos.description: Penn gets out in transition off a great hustle, and it turns into a Michael Wang 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Penn's Wang knocks down 3 after great hustle

videos.description: Penn guard Antonio Woods goes back door and finishes the tough layup plus the foul.
videos.headline: Penn's Woods finishes through contact

videos.description: Villanova forward Eric Paschall goes baseline for big time double-clutch dunk.
videos.headline: Paschall shows off athleticism with huge dunk

videos.description: Penn mistakenly throws the ball out of bounds on the inbounds pass but Phil Booth is unable to hit from 3 giving Penn the win over Villanova.
videos.headline: Penn almost makes monumental mistake, upsets No. 17 Nova

videos.description: Villanova tries to make a comeback against Penn, but the Quakers keep responding and come out with the 78-75 victory.
